<h1>🎯 Target board</h1>

<p>⭐ Draw a target board with concentric circles.</p>
<img src="samples/loops/img/target.svg" alt="Target board" />

<details>
  <summary>Hint</summary>
  <pre><code class="language-evy">//...
while r > ❓
    circle r
    r = ❓ - ❓
end
</code></pre>
</details>

<p>⭐ Animate the circles with a <code>sleep</code> for 0.2 seconds.</p>

<details>
  <summary>Hint</summary>
  <pre><code class="language-evy">//...
while r > ❓
    // ...
    sleep ❓
end
</code></pre>
</details>

<p>⭐ Increase the starting radius to cover the whole canvas.</p>
